Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • Item
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Commercial, Song, TalkShow

    public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
    This Class Is the Item Class of which child classes will inherit from It contains the general information for a particular item and upon instantiation will create An Item object that will allow you to manipulate said Items.
